<p><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/breach-of-union-rules-decision-tavsanoglu-v-gmb" class="govuk-link">Breach of union rules decision: Tavsanoglu v GMB (D/8/19-20)</a></p>

<p>Dr Tavsanoglu made a complaint of breach of union rule in relation to her alleged removal from office. The Certification Officer struck out the application under section 256ZA of the Trade Union and Labour Relations (Consolidation) Act 1992 on the basis that it has no reasonable prospect of success and/or is otherwise misconceived.</p>

